# ColorMix

Demo Video: https://youtu.be/XOdefqxCgGk

![DemoImage](DemoImage.png)

## Description
____________________________________________________
This is an IOS app where a random color is chosen.

* The user is given a red, green, and blue button to mix to match the color.
* Once the user is satisfied, they can click "check" to see if the color picked matches.
* Score is determined by how close the picked color is to the original.
* the checks limit the amount of colors that are allowed to be added before the game ends
* A timer counts down, and once it reaches zero, the game ends.

## Features
_______________________________________________________

Varying Difficulties
* Changes the timer and checks allowed per color
* How to play opens a window showing how to play the game.
